00:05:14.980 --> 00:05:17.660
So that gives you
1 in 100 million.

00:05:17.660 --> 00:05:20.130
So you're actually
twice-- almost,

00:05:20.130 --> 00:05:22.460
this is very rough--
you're roughly twice

00:05:22.460 --> 00:05:26.170
as likely to get struck by
